Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後然後  五班有個超可愛的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女生有那麼一點點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏目  你有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那雙清澈的眼睛直直的看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字不知道  因為她一句話都不說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裏  夏目？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說五班有個可愛女生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  趕快走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼夏目也要去？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走快點走快點  休息時間要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…啊  有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她  是她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  感覺好像有點陰沉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是看點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  站起來了  要出來咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是二班的西村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟你做個朋友啊…之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  她的確是看著我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎  你多心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
